        "name": "Mantis's Grasp",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You cause red, ghostly mantis arms to sprout from a nearby surface and crush a creature, dealing 8d6 force damage and attempting to pin the target in place. The effects are determined by the creature's Reflex save.",
